description:
Applicability
This optional schedule applies to general power use with a demand of less than 35 kW for the following: (1) commercial and industrial customers for general power use and (2) other services where other Rate Schedules (other than Rate Schedules NM and SG) do not apply. This schedule is applicable on an annual basis only.
name: Schedule CT Commercial Service - Time-Of-Use Under 35 kW
